msgid "# Set-ClusterQuorum"
msgstr "# 设置集群法定人数（Set-ClusterQuorum）"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Configures quorum options for a failover cluster."
msgstr "配置故障转移集群的法定人数（quorum）相关选项。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The `Set-ClusterQuorum` cmdlet configures quorum options for a failover cluster. The quorum\n"
"configuration in a failover cluster determines the number of failures that the cluster can sustain.\n"
"If an additional failure occurs, the cluster must stop running. The relevant failures in this\n"
"context are failures of nodes or, in some cases, of a disk witness (which contains a copy of the\n"
"cluster configuration) or file share witness."
msgstr ""
"`Set-ClusterQuorum` cmdlet "
"用于配置故障转移集群的法定人数（quorum）相关选项。在故障转移集群中，法定人数的设置决定了该集群能够承受的故障数量；如果再发生额外的故障，集群就必须停止运行。这里的“故障”指的是节点故障，或者在某些情况下，还包括磁盘见证（其中存储有集群配置的副本）或文件共享见证的故障。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1"
msgstr "### 示例 1"

msgid ""
"This example changes the quorum configuration to Node Majority on the local "
"cluster."
msgstr "这个示例将本地集群的投票机制（quorum configuration）更改为“节点多数制”（Node Majority）。"

msgid "### Example 2"
msgstr "### 示例 2"

msgid ""
"This example changes the quorum configuration to Node and Disk Majority on the local cluster, using\n"
"the disk resource named `Cluster Disk 7` for the disk witness."
msgstr ""
"这个示例将本地集群的法定人数（quorum）配置更改为“节点多数”（Node Majority）和“磁盘多数”（Disk "
"Majority），并使用名为“Cluster Disk 7”的磁盘资源作为磁盘见证者（disk witness）。"

msgid "### Example 3"
msgstr "### 示例 3"

msgid ""
"This example changes the quorum configuration to Node and File Share Majority on the local cluster,\n"
"using the disk resource at `\\\\fileserver\\fsw` for the file share witness."
msgstr ""
"这个示例将本地集群的法定人数（quorum）配置更改为“节点多数”（Node Majority）和“文件共享多数”（File Share "
"Majority），并使用位于 `\\\\fileserver\\fsw` 的磁盘资源作为文件共享见证节点。"

msgid "### Example 4"
msgstr "### 示例 4"

msgid ""
"This example changes the quorum configuration to use an Azure Storage Account to use as a Cloud\n"
"Witness."
msgstr "这个示例将法定人数（quorum）配置更改为使用一个Azure存储账户作为云见证（Cloud Witness）。"

msgid ""
"The example uses splatting to pass parameter values from the `$Parameters` variable to the command.\n"
"Learn more about [Splatting](/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_splatting)."
msgstr ""
"这个示例使用了“拆分”（splatting）技术，将 `$Parameters` 变量中的参数值传递给命令。有关 "
"[拆分](/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_splatting) "
"的更多信息，请参阅相关文档。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定要运行此cmdlet的集群名称。如果该参数的输入值为`.`或被省略，则cmdlet将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid ""
"Causes the cluster quorum to be set to disk only type. This isn't recommended as it creates a\n"
"single point of failure for the cluster."
msgstr "这会导致集群的法定人数（quorum）仅设置为基于磁盘存储的方式。这种设置并不推荐，因为它会为整个集群带来单点故障的风险。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the disk resource that the cluster quorum uses as the disk witness. Specifying\n"
"this parameter sets the cluster quorum to the Node and Disk Majority type."
msgstr ""
"指定集群法定人数（quorum）用作磁盘见证者（disk "
"witness）的磁盘资源名称。设置此参数后，集群法定人数的类型将变为“节点和磁盘多数制”（Node and Disk Majority）。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the path of the file share that the cluster quorum uses as the file witness. Specifying\n"
"this parameter sets the cluster quorum to the Node and File Share Majority type."
msgstr ""
"指定集群仲裁机制（quorum）用作“文件见证”（file "
"witness）的文件共享路径。设置此参数后，集群仲裁机制的模式将变为“节点和文件共享多数投票”（Node and File Share "
"Majority）类型。"

msgid "Specifies the cluster on which to change the quorum type."
msgstr "指定要更改仲裁团类型的集群。"

msgid ""
"Indicates that the cmdlet sets the cluster quorum to the Node Majority type."
msgstr "表示该cmdlet将集群法定人数（quorum）设置为“节点多数”（Node Majority）类型。"

